<section class="container mx-auto mt-16 px-6 py-12 rounded-xl shadow-md bg-white w-3/4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">About Us</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-8">ReMind is dedicated to providing comprehensive, compassionate care to individuals and families affected by dementia. We understand the challenges and offer personalized services that aim to improve the quality of life for both patients and caregivers.</p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-8">Our mission is to provide tailored support and resources for those living with dementia and their families. Through our services, we aim to bring comfort, security, and independence to individuals, ensuring they are well cared for at every stage of their journey.</p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Services</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-8">We offer a range of services including home-based care, medication reminders, appointment tracking, and caregiver support. Our team is experienced in managing various aspects of dementia care, and we collaborate with families to create a holistic care plan that fits each patient's needs.</p>
</section>

